embed.title: ASCENSION - League of Legends Xin Zhao Gameplay // Flow @ WalrossGaming
embed.description: Hello Guys and Welcome to my Channel. This is a full Gameplay of the League of Legends Mode ASCENSION with Champ Xin Zhao. (https://youtu.be/jVXw1WOB2sk) I really like this mode because it quite different from normals, ranked and ARAM but develops very strong action from the first Minute till the end of the Game.
